                        <interp inst="t18451027-name-423" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES RICHARDS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am porter to Mrs. Elizabeth Whitfield—about the 30th of Sept. she had some oil-cloth of this description—I missed it—I believe this to be it.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character, and a witness engaged to employ him.)</p>
